Battera::

She had to hide her true programs and make this look good.  She 
grinned evily. "Ah, yes. The terminations I have made. I killed a few 
maximals in my time. Not as many as you may have killed. No, my 
numbers would pale in comparison I'm afraid. I have killed to date, 
only 12 maximals. Well, I did say I was into more covert operations."
